<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="view-vt">view <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /vjuː/    美 /vjuː/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[正式用语] 看；观赏；观看：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>These mountains are a splendid sight when <strong>viewed from</strong> the valley floor.
从谷底看上去，群山壮丽。</p><footer>2005 山东</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-see">2.★ <strong>看待(see)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>view</strong> film <strong>as</strong> a type of contemporary art.
我们把电影视作一种当代艺术。</p><footer>译林⑧ – 4</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>viewer /'vjuːə(r)/ n [C]  </p></div>